Hello Parveen, I studied the report; it includes all of the necessary parts, but there are several areas for improvement. Here are some ideas I have to make the report better. 1. The executive summary is okay, but it can be enhanced to include information about your previous work, tools, and methods to solve the issue. 2. You have addressed business issues like limited seating space and no proper menu card in the proposal. What do you mean? How do you resolve this issue? There is no analysis related to that.In my opinion, you should focus more on the root issue of business. 3.Fig. 3.1 line graphs are poorly plotted and difficult to understand. Do not plot multiple datasets on a single graph. and most item colour lines are similar. 4. In Fig. 3.8, you need to give a reason why milk sales decreased to mid-January and then randomly increased. There is no explanation for the random fluctuation in sales. 5. The interpretation of results is fine, but recommendations could be improved.What do you mean by a recommendation like a proper menu card, menu adjustments, and limited seating space? There are no proper suggestions given by you. Your report does not cover all the issues raised in the proposal, so the report is not progressive. It has rejection criteria, but there is also no room for improvement. You chose the wrong problem statement, like a first problem and a second problem, in the proposal. You have done some work, so I will accept it but reduce your marks
